=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283e2551b4264ddffb63ae88391e0a44805deaea","tid":681089,"uid":175912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"屌老母，依家日日3字頭天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係搞唔撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8820bb2239342bf6a2ce29edb999bf4bd091445","tid":681089,"uid":187086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T03:08:05.000Z","msg":"有 去睇中醫 我3月起 宜加清到7788 要介多陣口 防止番發"},{"pid":"9e4bb013d2f370324df99bce81682686df831e6d","tid":681089,"uid":46083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"我條頸本身都有，之後忍唔住越r越多，老母買咗支嘢俾我搽同忍住唔r，兩星期好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bb5fa1b4694e768a74c7e58e9420abca65f7d0","tid":681089,"uid":187115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:21:22.000Z","msg":"呢排轉熱 出多左汗又會容易起疹<br />\n我會用天然D既止汗劑(有種礦物質叫明礬，天然抗菌止汗，可以google下)<br />\n唔係100%止汗 而係可以抗菌止癢先 收工返屋企即刻用手工皂沖涼<br />\n<br />\n食野方面唔食海鮮牛之外都唔食辣或太重口味既野<br />\n<br />\n咁樣會好D"},{"pid":"d47aa780e5dccfe02734420584bb28bb510f7a31","tid":681089,"uid":39728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"主要致敏嘅成因唔同人可能會差好遠<br />\n你唔介意咪試下大包圍先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就有次試到自己食蟹會周身痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保濕真係好重要<br />\n早排同事話Aveeno燕麥嗰支野好用<br />\n佢倒咗啲俾我我覺得真係唔錯<br />\n又無味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e873571b76d2f33f0aedfb01950e5570a00ffcb4","tid":681089,"uid":185377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"用凍水沖涼同食小啲重口味野，其實茶藥我覺得真係沒咩用，唯有好嚴重個陣先茶啲類固醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950566ab5e6309dc0a76a011b5d0df75e